	(text "Linear range (0-21V) IN: 21V -> OUT: 2Vpp\nLow acc. range (21-26V) IN: 26V -> OUT: 2.476Vpp\nMax. input voltage: 63V -> OUT: 2.49Vpp\n\nGain = 10k/(2x100k+10k)*2 = 0.09524\nFc = 80 Hz\nAccuracy: 1%-0.1% (depends on resistors' acc.)"
